citations:
  citation-awoiaf-harren-hoare:
    source: source-awoiaf
    properties:
      locator: "Harren Hoare"
      accessed: "2026-03-15"
    notes: "Died 2-1 BC at Harrenhal. Ironborn culture. House Hoare. Title: King of the Isles and the Rivers. Father: Halleck Hoare. Known as Harren the Black and Black Harren. Last King of the Isles and the Rivers. Completed Harrenhal, burned alive by Aegon I on Balerion."
